		{"id":"84a56830373dfbca","type":"text","text":"$X=R^n, \\tilde{X} = X\\times [\\infty, +\\infty]$\n$A$ is a preepi iff $A \\subset \\tilde{X}$.\nBut this should be check durring proof, and should be changed.","x":973,"y":235,"width":250,"height":130,"color":"1"},
