		{"id":"79b02eb5ddeceb7e","type":"text","text":"Should not use\n- $X \\times (-\\infty, +\\infty)$ does not cover indicator function\n- $X \\times (-\\infty, +\\infty]$ does not admit a $f =-\\infty$ (unit of join or meet) as a function","x":973,"y":560,"width":250,"height":264},
